                               [p_employ.jpg]

   To meet its statutory mission, the Office requires a highly dedicated
   and diverse staff to conduct audits, investigations, and inspections
   and evaluate programs and activities of the Department of Energy.

   The Office recruits professionals in the fields of accounting, finance,
   business, and public administration, computer science, law,
   administrative support, and other related fields.
